# Normalize line endings to LF in both the repo and the working tree. The repo
# builds with nvcc on Windows (A5000) and the Orin and has no CRLF-dependent
# tooling, so LF everywhere avoids the spurious "modified" diffs that core.autocrlf
# + cross-editor churn produce. Binaries are auto-detected and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
